---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Our Services - From Chaos to Operational Clarity',
  description: 'Three specialized services designed for asset-heavy operations: Trusted Reporting, Data Foundations, and Intelligent Automation.',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-24 pb-20 sm:pt-32 sm:pb-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-blue-50/30 to-orange-50/20 dark:from-slate-900 dark:via-slate-900 dark:to-slate-800"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-orange-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-orange-900/20 rounded-full mb-8 border border-orange-200/50 dark:border-orange-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <Icon name="tabler:route" class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400" />
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Our Services</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          From Spreadsheet Chaos to <br class="hidden lg:block"/>
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-orange-500">Operational Clarity</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Three specialized services designed for asset-heavy operations where decisions can't wait for standard IT timelines.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Operational Clarity Framework -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16 px-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="h-px w-12 bg-orange-600"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-orange-600">Our Methodology</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">The Path to Operational Clarity</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          A proven sequence designed to stabilize your current reporting, build a scalable foundation, and unlock high-value automation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Diagram Component -->
      <div class="mb-20 flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="relative group max-w-[1024px] w-full">
          <!-- Subtle glow effect -->
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/20 to-blue-500/20 rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-1000 group-hover:duration-200"></div>
          
          <div class="relative bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-2 shadow-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
            <img
              src="/images/homepage-hero.png"
              alt="From Data Chaos to Operational Clarity Frameowrk"
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-2 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-full border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50">
          <Icon name="tabler:info-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400" />
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 italic">
            Each layer requires the foundation below to be solid — you can't skip steps.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Service Details -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="h-px w-12 bg-orange-600"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-orange-600">Service Details</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">What Each Service Delivers</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Service 1: Trusted Reporting -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-red-100 dark:border-red-900/30 hover:border-red-300 dark:hover:border-red-700 transition-all hover:shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <Icon name="tabler:target-arrow" class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400" />
          </div>

          <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-red-600 mb-2">Step 1: Stabilize</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Trusted Reporting</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4 italic">"For teams drowning in spreadsheet reconciliation."</p>

          <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            ⏱ Delivered in 2-3 weeks
          </div>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">What You Get</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Single source of operational truth</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Automated weekly/daily updates</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Clear data ownership rules</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Dashboards leadership uses</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
              <Icon name="tabler:arrow-up-right" class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Real Impact:</strong> Month-end close reduced from 5 days to 4 hours.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 2: Data Foundations -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-900/30 hover:border-blue-300 dark:hover:border-blue-700 transition-all hover:shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <Icon name="tabler:database" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" />
          </div>

          <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-blue-600 mb-2">Step 2: Build</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Data Foundations</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4 italic">"For companies outgrowing spreadsheets."</p>

          <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            ⏱ Timeline assessed in discovery
          </div>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">What You Get</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Modern cloud lakehouse architecture</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Governed data with access controls</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Integration with ERP & systems</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Scalable foundation for AI</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
              <Icon name="tabler:arrow-up-right" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Real Impact:</strong> 7 data sources unified into single governed platform.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 3: Intelligent Automation -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-green-100 dark:border-green-900/30 hover:border-green-300 dark:hover:border-green-700 transition-all hover:shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <Icon name="tabler:brain" class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" />
          </div>

          <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-green-600 mb-2">Step 3: Optimize</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Intelligent Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4 italic">"Only after foundations are trusted."</p>

          <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            ⏱ Custom timeline per use case
          </div>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-3">What You Get</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Demand forecasting models</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Anomaly detection systems</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Automated workflow optimization</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
                <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                <span>Production-ready ML models</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm">
              <Icon name="tabler:arrow-up-right" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Real Impact:</strong> Equipment anomalies detected 48 hours before failure.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Decision Framework -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Which Service Do You Need?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          Not sure where to start? Here's how similar energy and industrial teams typically engage with us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-8 border-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <div class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">If you're here:</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6">
            "We debate numbers in every meeting. Leadership doesn't trust our reports. Excel is breaking."
          </p>
          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
            <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Start with:</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-bold text-red-600">Trusted Reporting</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-8 border-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <div class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">If you're here:</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6">
            "Reports are okay, but data is scattered everywhere. We can't scale. Every ask is custom work."
          </p>
          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
            <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Start with:</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-600">Data Foundations</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">Timeline assessed after discovery</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-8 border-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <div class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">If you're here:</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6">
            "Our data is clean and trusted. Now we want predictive insights, automation, and smarter operations."
          </p>
          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
            <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Start with:</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-bold text-green-600">Intelligent Automation</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">Custom scope & timeline</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a
          href="mailto:ethiraj.k@dataadvisors.ai"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-orange-500 hover:from-orange-700 hover:to-orange-600 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-orange-500/25 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-orange-500/40 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
        >
          Book a Strategy Call
          <Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
